[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+     60[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m4[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mThe premature-death-report-reversal pathway is the recipe's most consequential cryptographic-and-operational ceremony.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The reversal is the operation that restores a wrongly-applied death status; the reversal also affects every downstream system that consumed the wrongly-applied status. A forged reversal (an attacker who has compromised the reversal-operator role's execution context; a single-actor approval that bypasses dual-control; a reversal triggered for an actually-deceased patient that re-activates the patient's records and triggers unauthorized post-death disclosure) silently re-activates a deceased patient or, worse, fails to reverse a wrongly-applied death status leaving the affected patient experiencing the prolonged-disruption the recipe correctly elevates as acutely negative. The Step 6 pseudocode validates the verifier's authorization and the dual-control approval, but the architecture does not specify the dual-control mechanism (cross-account approval through a separate approval-workflow Lambda; two operators from non-overlapping organizational units enforced through cross-account IAM roles; the architecture rejects single-actor approvals), the audit-log replication SLA before the reversal completes (the audit log is replicated to the dedicated audit account with a verified completion signal before the reversal is committed), the cascade-reversal coordinator that drives the per-system reversal sequence (each cascade consumer has its own reversal protocol; the reversal coordinator operates against each consumer in sequence with audit logging on every step), or the family-communication-during-reversal framework (the patient is contacted during reversal with the institutional explanation and the corrective-action timeline; the post-reversal operational-quality review is initiated within 5 business days). The recipe's own Production-Gaps TODO at the reversal pathway paragraph specifies these elements explicitly but the architecture pattern does not actually adopt them.[K
