r-source quality-drift-triggered re-classification), audit logs are stored with the framework's specified retention floor. Audit logs are stored with Object Lock in Compliance mode for immutability and a lifecycle policy transitioning to S3 Glacier Deep Archive after 90 days for cost optimization. CloudTrail data events are forwarded to a dedicated audit AWS account in the institution's organization, isolating the audit substrate from the production data plane. The retention floor is enforced at the bucket-policy and Object-Lock-configuration level, not at application logic."[38;2;180;142;173m*[K
