[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    441[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mLocation:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Honest Take's opening trap paragraph: "The trap most specific to deceased-patient resolution is treating it as a data-integration project. The data-integration is necessary but not sufficient. The pipeline is fundamentally about how the institution behaves toward families during one of the most emotionally-significant moments those families experience; the engineering is in service of that behavior, not the other way around. The institutions that succeed in deceased-patient resolution treat it as a family-experience-and-institutional-dignity program with the engineering as its substrate; the institutions that treat it as an engineering project produce technically-correct pipelines that nonetheless generate the wrong-patient correspondence the family experiences as an institutional failure."[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    442[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mNote:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m This is the right elevation for deceased-patient resolution specifically. In 5.7 the dignity framing is the load-bearing observation; in 5.8 the trust-framework-first observation is the engineering-discipline framing; in 5.9 the QHIN-onboarding-is-the-starting-line observation is the institutional-discipline framing; in 5.10 the family-experience-and-institutional-dignity-program-with-engineering-as-substrate observation is the moral-discipline framing that the rest of the architecture serves. The chapter editor should preserve this framing through the editing pass.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    443[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    444[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;143;161;179m###[38;2;192;197;206m [38;2;143;161;179mFinding V6: The Closing "Engineering Serves the Framing" Line Is the Chapter's Strongest Single Final Architectural-and-Philosophical Statement[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    445[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    446[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mSeverity:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m None (positive observation)[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    447[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mExpert:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Voice[K
