[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    519[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The opening Marisol-with-the-fourteen-page-PDF vignette earns its position as the chapter's strongest single articulation of the form-based-intake-failure-mode.** The text-message Monday morning, the lunch-break completion attempt, the eighty-six-checkbox review of systems, the 14% phone battery, the two-line chief complaint, the "father - heart attack age 51" family-history line that loses the paternal-grandfather-at-forty-eight detail, the fifteen-minute appointment that runs over because the form's data was thin enough that Dr. Adekunle re-asks everything, and the constellation of features (chest tightness plus exertional pattern plus family history of early heart disease) that an experienced clinical assistant would chase with adaptive follow-ups but the form does not are the recipe's clearest articulation of the existing-form-based-system-fails-the-patient-and-the-clinician primitive.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    520[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "what makes a great intake is not what makes a great form" framing is the recipe's strongest single passage on the form-versus-conversation primitive.** The "the next question is not 'any history of measles?' The next question is 'tell me more about that. When does it happen? What does it feel like?'" framing earns its position.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    521[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "by turn fourteen, the bot has the kind of HPI that an experienced triage nurse would have collected" pivot from individual vignette into the modern-bot-experience is the recipe's strongest single passage on the technology-actually-works-now-for-the-clinician primitive.**
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    522[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "is and is not" enumeration earns its position** as the recipe's clearest articulation of the bot-scope-as-discipline primitive in adaptive-interview context: "It is not the diagnostician. It is not the triage bot. It is not a replacement for the visit. It is not an open-ended conversational therapy bot. It is not a regulatory medical-device-style decision-support tool." This positioning is recipe-distinct and load-bearing.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    523[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "the bot's quality is bounded above by the practice's intake-protocol explicitness and the chart-context completeness" framing earns its position** as the recipe's strongest single articulation of the protocol-as-quality-ceiling primitive in adaptive-interview context.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    524[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The Technology section's "Why a Generic LLM Cannot Run a Pre-Visit Intake" subsection's seven-property enumeration is recipe-distinct** and earns its position as the recipe's clearest articulation of the why-naked-LLM-in-front-of-intake-conversation-is-not-an-intake-bot primitive.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    525[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "What the Intake Bot Has To Do That the Refill Bot Did Not" subsection's five-property enumeration** is the recipe's clearest articulation of the adaptive-interview-bot-vs-clinical-action-bot-distinction primitive.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    526[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "Intake Reality" subsection's twelve-property enumeration earns its position** as the recipe's most-distinctive contribution. The visit-types-are-not-interchangeable observation, the chief-complaints-open-ended-and-protocol-must-adapt observation, the patients-answer-in-unexpected-ways observation, the patient's-free-text-answer-often-contains-multiple-findings observation, the screeners-are-sensitive-instruments observation (with the PHQ-9 item 9 framing), the cultural-and-linguistic-variability-in-symptom-expression observation, the patients-sometimes-disclose-sensitive-information-unexpectedly observation, the medication-reconciliation-discrepancies-are-common observation, the family-history-accuracy-is-variable observation, the intake-conversation-is-asynchronous-and-may-be-interrupted observation, the bot-is-sometimes-the-patient's-first-encounter-with-the-practice observation, and the pediatric-and-proxy-completion-flows-are-common observation are each the recipe's right register.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    527[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Self-deprecating expertise lands well throughout the Honest Take.** The "the intake bot is the recipe in this chapter where the patient-experience improvement is most immediately visible, the clinical-data-quality improvement is most measurable per visit, and the institutional-maturity required is most spread across multiple clinical and operational teams" framing is the recipe's clearest articulation of the institutional-maturity-spread-across-multiple-teams primitive.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    528[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The Honest Take's eight-trap enumeration is well-chosen.** The second trap (validated-screener-as-loose-conversational-topics with the paraphrasing-invalidates-the-score framing) and the third trap (crisis-and-acuity-layer-as-add-it-later with the highest-density-disclosure-surface framing) are the recipe's strongest single traps.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    529[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "thing that surprises engineers" / "thing that surprises clinical leaders" cross-discipline-comparisons earn their positions.** The clinical-leaders-coming-from-clinical-software-backgrounds observation about "how much of the bot's value comes from the LLM's ability to follow the patient's thread" with the "the patients perceive the bot as listening, not just collecting" framing is the recipe's strongest single passage on the LLM-natural-language-understanding-as-patient-experience-improvement primitive.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    530[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "the thing about" vendor-honest assessments are the right register.** The Bedrock observation, the cost observation, the clinical-safety observation, and the patient-experience observation are each the recipe's right register.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    531[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **The "the thing I would do differently the second time: invest more, earlier, in the per-visit-type protocol formalization, and start with fewer visit types" earns its position** as the chapter's analog of the self-deprecating-expertise-with-actionable-takeaway register.
