[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    629[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Recipe 11.4 is publishable at the medium-tier level once the three HIGH findings are closed. The Honest Take is the recipe's strongest single passage and the chapter's strongest single articulation of the institutional-maturity-spread-across-multiple-teams primitive in adaptive-interview context. The "Marisol deserves a better intake experience than the fourteen-page form, and Dr. Adekunle deserves a structured pre-visit packet that lets her spend her fifteen minutes on what matters most" framing matches the chapter pattern from 11.1, 11.2, and 11.3 while elevating the recipe-distinct adaptive-interview contributions.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    630[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    631[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The recipe-specific contributions that should be elevated to the chapter preface as load-bearing primitives are: (a) the **per-visit-type intake-protocol-as-code-with-versioned-governance primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing for any adaptive-interview conversational AI recipe; the protocol is the bot's clinical-record-quality ceiling); (b) the **validated-screener-library-governed-separately primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; paraphrasing the items invalidates the score; modifying screener wordings is a governance event not a software change); (c) the **acuity-pattern-library-with-named-patient-safety-committee-ownership primitive** (recipe-distinct, load-bearing; the patient-safety committee owns the pattern library with quarterly review cadence and tabletop drills); (d) the **crisis-and-acuity-flagging-as-parallel-pipeline-architectural-floor primitive** (recipe-distinct; the pipeline is a separate component, not a feature of the conversational LLM, because the consequences of missing a crisis signal are severe); (e) the **medication-and-allergy-reconciliation-do-not-modify-chart primitive** (recipe-distinct; the bot captures patient-reported deltas as structured events, not chart changes); (f) the **conversation-log-as-rich-PHI-and-clinical-record primitive** (recipe-distinct; many institutions treat the log as part of the formal medical record); (g) the **pre-visit-packet-as-clinical-team-facing-contract primitive** (recipe-distinct; the schema is the bot's clinical-team-facing contract, owned by clinical informatics); (h) the **EHR-side-packet-display-as-deployment-prerequisite primitive** (recipe-distinct; a beautiful packet that lands in a part of the EHR no clinician reads is worthless); (i) the **resumability-as-architectural-primitive** (recipe-distinct; patients fill out intake on lunch breaks, on phones with low batteries, in distracted environments); (j) the **per-cohort-mis-extraction-rate-as-clinical-record-quality-acute-metric primitive** (recipe-distinct; HPI-and-ROS-and-medication-and-allergy mis-extraction has clinical-record-quality consequences); (k) the **Marisol-and-Dr.-Adekunle-as-canonical-user-and-clinician primitive** (recipe-distinct; building the bot well for both Marisol and Dr. Adekunle is the recipe's moral case); (l) the **engineering-teams-that-treat-it-as-clinical-team-facing-product-ship-a-bot-the-clinicians-actually-consume primitive** (recipe-distinct; the bot's value is the clinical team's experience of consuming the structured packet, not the engineering team's experience of building the chat surface).
